nmap2nagios-ng v0.1.3
==================

DESCRIPTION
===========
nmap2nagios-ng is a script for generating Nagios host, hostgroup and services configuration files from Nmap XML output.
You can choose if configuration files for Nagios 2.x or Nagios 3.x will be created. 

There is embedded POD documentation in nmap2nagios-ng.pl, just type perldoc nmap2nagios-ng.pl

This software is tested with Nmap 4.53!!

